nodes.text: The Art of War (Star Wars Insider 89)

The Art of War is an article published in Star Wars Insider 89 and Star Wars: The Official Magazine 66 written by Frank Parisi and illustrated by Jan Duursema, responsible for the artwork of the Star Wars: Legacy comics. Jan Duursema is quoted throughout the article as she explains the influences and techniques used for designing Star Wars: Legacy.
